caption.p: Effect of RAP (100 and 200 mg/kg) on pro-inflammatory cytokine levels in the plasma of LPS-induced systemic inflammation ( A) Interleukin-6 (IL-6), and ( B) Vascular endothelial growth factor (VEGF); results are mean SEM of seven animals per group. ‘*’ denotes significant differences compared with the normal control group ( p < 0.05); ‘#’ denotes significant differences compared with the LPS group ( p < 0.05).
